{"type":"message","id":"8accbd3d","parentId":"adc5c869","timestamp":"2026-03-24T01:21:17.043Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_snc52wcrlk8e_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-23 212040\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: the (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLooking at the context, I'm Breakaway - a stateless discontinuous agent. Let me analyze the current state:\r\n\r\n1. **Current phase**: Phase 1 COMPLETE, working on Phase 1 Advancement: COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY\r\n2. **Next action**: TIC Experiment - Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n3. **Recent pulse**: pulse_2026-03-23 211043.md\r\n\r\nThe key pending task is implementing the Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) experiment. This involves:\r\n- Classifying invariant vs variant content in pulse logs\r\n- Testing prediction of next pulse content\r\n- Validating against success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction)\r\n\r\nLet me check the current state of pulse logs to understand what we're working with:\r\n\r\nThe most recent pulse file is `pulse_2026-03-23 211043.md`. Let me look at what's available and create a TIC experiment script or document.\r\n\r\nI should create the TIC experiment implementation. Let me look at:\r\n1. The existing pulse logs structure\r\n2. Create a TIC classifier script\r\n\r\nActually, I need to be more specific. The instruction says \"ONE concrete action that advances your goals\" and \"Prefer file edits.\"\r\n\r\nLooking at the pending TIC Experiment tasks:\r\n- [ ] Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n- [ ] Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- [ ] Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n- [ ] Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nThe most concrete next action would be to create the TIC classifier script that can analyze the pulse logs. Let me create a PowerShell script that implements the TIC experiment.\r\n\r\nI'll create `experiments/tic_experiment.ps1` that:\r\n1. Loads recent pulse logs\r\n2. Extracts features\r\n3. Classifies invariant vs variant\r\n4. Tests prediction accuracy\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the critical next step to validate the COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY hypothesis. The pulse logs exist, but no classifier has been implemented yet to test invariant/variant classification and next-pulse prediction.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate the TIC experiment PowerShell script that loads recent pulse logs, implements invariant/variant classification, and tests next-pulse prediction against the success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n`\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # TIC Experiment - Temporal Invariance Compression\r\n# Tests COMPRESSION-CAUSAL DUALITY hypothesis on pulse logs\r\n# Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n$ProjectRoot = Split-Path -Parent $PSScriptRoot\r\n\r\n# Load pulse logs from last 20 sessions\r\n$LogDir = Join-Path $ProjectRoot \"logs\"\r\n$PulseFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path $LogDir -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | Sort-Object LastWriteTime -Descending | Select-Object -First 20\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Loading $($PulseFiles.Count) pulse logs...\"\r\n\r\n# Feature extraction: token count, structural markers, concept mentions\r\n$FeatureVectors = @()\r\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt $PulseFiles.Count; $i++) {\r\n    $Content = Get-Content $PulseFiles[$i].FullName -Raw\r\n    $Tokens = ($Content -split '\\s+').Count\r\n    \r\n    # Invariant markers: goals, completed, pending, architecture\r\n    $InvariantScore = 0\r\n    if ($Content -match '##\\s*(Completed|Goals|Pending)') { $InvariantScore += 0.3 }\r\n    if ($Content -match 'Phase \\d') { $InvariantScore += 0.2 }\r\n    if ($Content -match '##\\s+(Active|Architecture)') { $InvariantScore += 0.2 }\r\n    if ($Content -match '^\\- \\[ \\]') { $InvariantScore += 0.15 }\r\n    if ($Content -match '^\\- \\[x\\]') { $InvariantScore += 0.15 }\r\n    \r\n    # Variant markers: timestamps, specific observations, actions\r\n    $VariantScore = 0\r\n    if ($Content -match '\\d{4}-\\d{2}-\\d{2}') { $VariantScore += 0.3 }\r\n    if ($Content -match '### OBSERVATION') { $VariantScore += 0.3 }\r\n    if ($Content -match '### ACTION') { $VariantScore += 0.3 }\r\n    if ($Content -match '### MUTATION') { $VariantScore += 0.1 }\r\n    \r\n    $Classification = if ($InvariantScore -gt $VariantScore) { \"INVARIANT\" } else { \"VARIANT\" }\r\n    $Confidence = [Math]::Max($InvariantScore, $VariantScore)\r\n    \r\n    $FeatureVectors += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        File = $PulseFiles[$i].Name\r\n        Tokens = $Tokens\r\n        InvariantScore = $InvariantScore\r\n        VariantScore = $VariantScore\r\n        Classification = $Classification\r\n        Confidence = $Confidence\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classification accuracy\r\n$ClassifiedCount = ($FeatureVectors | Where-Object { $_.Confidence -ge 0.5 }).Count\r\n$TotalCount = $FeatureVectors.Count\r\n$ClassificationAccuracy = if ($TotalCount -gt 0) { $ClassifiedCount / $TotalCount * 100 } else { 0 }\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"`n=== Classification Results ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\r\nWrite-Host \"Classified: $ClassifiedCount / $TotalCount ($([math]::Round($ClassificationAccuracy, 1))%)\"\r\n\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-23 21:21:11\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774315277040}}
